content:
Use Vlocity Insurance Group Benefits in the package data model to create quotes, manage plans and censuses, and enroll employees.

Trying to figure out which data model to use? The Salesforce data model is the digital insurance platform of choice. It uses harmonized services that integrate seamlessly into the Salesforce Customer 360 platform. If you're an existing customer who uses the package data model, plan to harmonize your data soon.

Insurance provides a streamlined quoting process for proposed prices of insurance products and services, for either a new opportunity or an existing customer.
Make group benefits enrollment a breeze with Vlocity Insurance enrollment features and services.
A census provides a statistical snapshot of the eligible members of a group (for example, employees) and their legal dependents. You can use a census for group benefits quoting and rating as well as the subsequent enrollment process.
title: Salesforce Insurance Group Benefits
